#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.shift.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.shift"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift:1 of
msgid "Shift index by desired number of periods with an optional time `freq`."
msgstr "根据指定的周期数以及可选的时间频率 `freq` 对索引进行偏移。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift:3 of
msgid ""
"When `freq` is not passed, shift the index without realigning the data. "
"If `freq` is passed (in this case, the index must be date or datetime, or"
" it will raise a `NotImplementedError`), the index will be increased "
"using the periods and the `freq`."
msgstr ""
"当未提供 `freq` 参数时，不重新对齐数据，仅偏移索引。如果提供了 `freq` "
"参数（此时索引必须为日期或日期时间类型，否则会抛出 `NotImplementedError`"
"），则将根据指定周期和频率 `freq` 来增加索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift:8 of
msgid "Number of periods to shift. Can be positive or negative."
msgstr "要偏移的周期数。可以为正数或负数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift:10 of
msgid ""
"Offset to use from the tseries module or time rule (e.g. 'EOM'). If "
"`freq` is specified then the index values are shifted but the data is not"
" realigned. That is, use `freq` if you would like to extend the index "
"when shifting and preserve the original data."
msgstr ""
"使用 tseries 模块中的偏移量或时间规则（例如 'EOM'）。如果指定了 `freq`，"
"则索引值会偏移但数据不会重新对齐。也就是说，如果希望在偏移时扩展索引并"
"保留原始数据，请使用 `freq`。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift:15 of
msgid "Shift direction."
msgstr "偏移方向。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift:17 of
msgid ""
"The scalar value to use for newly introduced missing values. the default "
"depends on the dtype of `self`. For numeric data, ``np.nan`` is used. For"
" datetime, timedelta, or period data, etc. :attr:`NaT` is used. For "
"extension dtypes, ``self.dtype.na_value`` is used."
msgstr ""
"用于新增缺失值的标量值。默认值取决于 `self` 的数据类型。对于数值型数据，"
"使用 ``np.nan``；对于日期时间、时间差或周期类型数据等，使用 :attr:`NaT`；"
"对于扩展数据类型，则使用 ``self.dtype.na_value``。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift:24 of
msgid "Copy of input object, shifted."
msgstr "输入对象的副本，已偏移。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Index.shift`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift:30 of
msgid "Shift values of Index."
msgstr "对 Index 的值进行偏移。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift:32 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DatetimeIndex.shift`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift:33 of
msgid "Shift values of DatetimeIndex."
msgstr "对 DatetimeIndex 的值进行偏移。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift:35 of
msgid ":py:obj:`PeriodIndex.shift`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift:36 of
msgid "Shift values of PeriodIndex."
msgstr "对 PeriodIndex 的值进行偏移。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift:38 of
msgid ":py:obj:`tshift`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.shift.shift:39 of
msgid "Shift the time index, using the index's frequency if available."
msgstr "对时间索引进行偏移，如果可用则使用索引的频率。"

